@page "/about"

<section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>

        <!-- First Row: Text on the left, Image on the right -->
        <div class="about-row">
            <div class="text-box fade-in">
                <h2>Who are we?</h2>
                <p>Num Num was founded in 2019 by a mother of two young children. Our mission is to provide delicious, nutritious meals made with love from our kitchen to yours.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image fade-in">
                <img src="/Assets/NumNumSign.jpg" alt="Who we are image" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Second Row: Image on the left, Text on the right -->
        <div class="about-row reverse">
            <div class="about-image fade-in">
                <img src="/Assets/NumNumKids.jpg" alt="What we do image" />
            </div>
            <div class="text-box fade-in">
                <h2>Why we do what we do</h2>
                <p>We focus on developing meals free from preservatives, salt, and sugar, encouraging baby-led weaning. Our baby-led weaning range supports texture exploration and chewing development.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Third Row: Text on the left, Image on the right -->
        <div class="about-row">
            <div class="text-box fade-in">
                <h2>How it works</h2>
                <p>All our meals are frozen to preserve freshness and nutrition. We design them with balanced protein, starch, and veggies, ensuring the best for your baby.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image fade-in">
                <img src="/Assets/NumNumCook.jpg" alt="How it works image" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>